{"tid":2128527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首闖禍 港人埋單  全禁堂食 限聚二人 戶外戴罩","createTime":"2020-07-28T04:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T04:52:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e5a43a12440e80e2f1b7b76890e7b7cb56bde9","tid":2128527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200728/C57WV2KITQ674UIDSOCCAMLKQ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FC57WV2KITQ674UIDSOCCAMLKQ4%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBgi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=69b4ea10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FC57WV2KITQ674UIDSOCCAMLKQ4%2F&h=6d5662c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200728/C57WV2KITQ674UIDSOCCAMLKQ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n特首闖禍 港人埋單 <br />\n全禁堂食 限聚二人 戶外戴罩<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上月還自詡成功遏止武漢肺炎大流行的特首林鄭月娥，在確診個案再創單日新高的同日，差遣副手、政務司長張建宗面對傳媒，宣佈進一步收緊防疫措施 ，包括食肆全日禁堂食、限聚令收緊至上限兩人、不論在室內或室外公眾地方要戴口罩等，嚴重影響民生。有醫生批評政府防疫失策拒絕認錯，卻要全港市民及醫護埋單。<br />\n<br />\n記者：李詠希 謝明明 王春怡<br />\n<br />\n有關措施今晚午夜12時起生效，為期七日至8月4日。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者多番追問多名專家早已指出豁免檢疫是這輪疫潮元凶，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新的防疫措施今晚午夜12時起生效，市民在戶外亦須戴口罩，吸煙亦不能獲豁免。<br />\n張建宗：可到郊野公園進食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：許樹昌轟政府經濟凌駕抗疫<br />\n<br />\n有記者追問食肆全面禁止堂食，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於早前有人提出推行「禁足令」或「居家令」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府會否向受影響行業作補償，張建宗無正面回應，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷批評，政府放寬船員免檢疫，如今「搞出個超級大頭佛」，要全港市民和醫護一同埋單，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">如政府堅稱豁免32類入境人士檢疫是必須，否則會對貨物、經濟有影響，那便應繼續豁免，「如果唔係點解以前做唔到收緊𠵱家又做到？」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NtlTSGTtYdZC5oNyH2Nm4ISeRJA=/818x1146/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LM6WRYARMCOUGL4LV5ZTI2FLRU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNtlTSGTtYdZC5oNyH2Nm4ISeRJA%3D%2F818x1146%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLM6WRYARMCOUGL4LV5ZTI2FLRU.gif&h=9c112acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員促推防疫基金助各行業<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員郭家麒亦。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員黃碧雲亦批評，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qmS7AenGFM6dpXZnjCEdWu26df8=/510x1089/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EG2EM3LV4UAMPYUDVDEYUGVDTE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqmS7AenGFM6dpXZnjCEdWu26df8%3D%2F510x1089%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEG2EM3LV4UAMPYUDVDEYUGVDTE.gif&h=91bfb193&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3015a7e3cf96b725932e1d91e72c48dd3babfef","tid":2128527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">如政府堅稱豁免32類入境人士檢疫是必須，否則會對貨物、經濟有影響，那便應繼續豁免，「如果唔係點解以前做唔到收緊𠵱家又做到？」</span></span>"},{"pid":"178c47a3c56df9250d26979bc58f0e5992eacb89","tid":2128527,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d566ecf025f92de6ce8f52d43ea1b4a4465ef4b1","tid":2128527,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:43:21.000Z","msg":"鄭月俄 殺人兇手"},{"pid":"b75ce4d022e27f9f7c8e3355a2015c4a68dbb6e1","tid":2128527,"uid":139438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:44:38.000Z","msg":"老母湊一對仔女都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8556de3069fd1c3d68707a388c29bb64a0533c25","tid":2128527,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75ce4d022e27f9f7c8e3355a2015c4a68dbb6e1","tid":2128527,"uid":139438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T04:44